{"tid":353403,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"【Orage台】怎樣才可以把一個遊戲愈玩愈廢? Day83 9/8","createTime":"2017-08-09T14:29:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-09T17:19:48.000Z","uid":122942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5e4675af80e021d553e87a3209a3c24c80255c82","tid":353403,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T14:29:05.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/5ADqP2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2F5ADqP2.gif&h=8c5a58f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家好，我係Orage。 我會於每晚11點至2點開台玩遊戲同與觀眾聊天。<br />\n因為我極度3分鐘熱度，所以好少會一直玩同一隻Game。<br />\n有興趣嘅巴打入黎捧下場，一齊傾下計啦  <br />\n<br />\n今晚11點左右見 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/oragejan \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitch.tv%2Foragejan%20&d=DJesqidDmerScbpUKvI81jCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=5e7ac9b2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.twitch.tv/oragejan </a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/W4CK8P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FW4CK8P.png&h=69cccb5f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n另外我開左個FB專頁，開台前或者有任何突發事唔開都會Po上FB。<br />\n有時會PO日常野同覺得有趣嘅事，希望巴打們可以入黎比個讚。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/oragejan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Foragejan&d=DJesqidDmerScbpUKvI81jCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=e5e1a345\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/oragejan</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/NRSeWz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FNRSeWz.jpg&h=f4a261d8&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n另外我亦開左個Youtuber Page放開台嘅Backup<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCa49ivSXtdCYwObEq9pRLSg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCa49ivSXtdCYwObEq9pRLSg&d=DJesqidDmerScbpUKvI81jCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=58660609\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCa49ivSXtdCYwObEq9pRLSg</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">請各位多多支持，比D錢黎洗下</span></span></div>"},{"pid":"5d977d447560f270a8c3265867972256b2d4cee4","tid":353403,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T15:11:56.000Z","msg":"已開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32af86220ebe42db63da1a6856a45d5153f9e7b3","tid":353403,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T15:12:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c17b79f9fe3f7661202efa0628396e6fab17fb62","tid":353403,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T15:12:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aca28a53216589d63586726efa1837d902a0551f","tid":353403,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T15:13:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fedab3f259838ee5234fda0ad165f7ba3b43de11","tid":353403,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T15:17:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6bd09a381e3aef895d41a678f0f242b1a760f42","tid":353403,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T15:21:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27c63c2a9789993c0b762cbe4a7c440748d35138","tid":353403,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T15:22:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78bfdfe70a8e19669472ac10640d5d49e5fbdde6","tid":353403,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T15:25:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=